<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Welcome to MindFull on MindFull Documentation</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/</link><description>Recent content in Welcome to MindFull on MindFull Documentation</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Architecture</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/development/architecture/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/development/architecture/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull is designed with two core principles: &lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven UI&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Security by Default&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-hybrid-data-architecture"&gt;1. Hybrid Data Architecture&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-hybrid-data-architecture"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We strictly separate static data from dynamic user engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="data-storage-strategy"&gt;Data Storage Strategy&lt;a class="anchor" href="#data-storage-strategy"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Category&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Storage Location&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Usage&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global UI Labels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;data/labels.json&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Buttons, navigation, and component text&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Static Content&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;content/*.md&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Blog posts, lessons, and course curriculum&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance Data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;data/cookies.json&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Legal transparency and consent manager&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engagement Data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;cms/db/mindfull.sqlite&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Views, Ratings, Comments, and Reactions&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Auth Sessions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;JWT + &lt;code&gt;localStorage&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Secure identity management&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3 id="dynamic-engagement-system"&gt;Dynamic Engagement System&lt;a class="anchor" href="#dynamic-engagement-system"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Node.js CMS manages real-time interactions using an optimized SQLite backend:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Branding</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/design/branding/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/design/branding/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull is designed to be reskinned in seconds while maintaining elite-level visual polish through centralized configuration and global smoothing engines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-core-visuals"&gt;1. Core Visuals&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-core-visuals"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="branding-configuration"&gt;Branding Configuration&lt;a class="anchor" href="#branding-configuration"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Property&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;File&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Value Type&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Logo Icon&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;FontAwesome Class&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Primary icon for header/footer (GPG signed)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Site Title&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Your organization&amp;rsquo;s name&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Color&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Hex Code&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Brand identity color (Indigo default)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Secondary Color&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Hex Code&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Accent color (Emerald default)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-high-fidelity-rendering"&gt;2. High-Fidelity Rendering&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-high-fidelity-rendering"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MindFull includes a built-in &lt;strong&gt;Smoothing Stack&lt;/strong&gt; that ensures your brand looks sharp on all displays.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Installation</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/getting-started/installation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/getting-started/installation/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Follow these steps to get your local development environment up and running.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-prerequisites"&gt;1. Prerequisites&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-prerequisites"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote class='book-hint note'&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure you have the following tools installed before proceeding.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Tool&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Version&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Purpose&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hugo (Extended)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;v0.120.0+&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Static Site Generation&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Node.js&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;v18.0.0+&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;CSS &amp;amp; Backend execution&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;npm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;v9.0.0+&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Dependency management&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3 id="readiness-checklist"&gt;Readiness Checklist&lt;a class="anchor" href="#readiness-checklist"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Hugo Extended installed (&lt;code&gt;hugo version&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Node.js installed (&lt;code&gt;node -v&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; npm installed (&lt;code&gt;npm -v&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-clone-and-install"&gt;2. Clone and Install&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-clone-and-install"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Clone the repository&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;git clone https://github.com/Obsidian-Solutions/self-help.git
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd self-help
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Install dependencies&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;npm install&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="3-initialize-the-cms"&gt;3. Initialize the CMS&lt;a class="anchor" href="#3-initialize-the-cms"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CMS handles authentication and secure content storage.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Quizzes</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/features/quizzes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/features/quizzes/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull includes a powerful client-side quiz engine. Quizzes are defined directly in the frontmatter of any lesson file.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-quick-start-checklist"&gt;1. Quick Start Checklist&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-quick-start-checklist"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Create a new lesson in &lt;code&gt;content/lessons/&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Define the &lt;code&gt;quiz&lt;/code&gt; block in frontmatter.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Add at least one question with options.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Set the &lt;code&gt;correct&lt;/code&gt; index (0-3).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Provide an explanation for the answer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-frontmatter-schema"&gt;2. Frontmatter Schema&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-frontmatter-schema"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;quiz&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Basics of CBT&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;description&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Test your knowledge of Cognitive Behavioral Therapy.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;result_message&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Great work! You&amp;#39;ve mastered the basics.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;questions&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;question&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;What does the &amp;#39;C&amp;#39; in CBT stand for?&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;options&lt;/span&gt;: [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Care&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Cognitive&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Change&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Center&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;correct&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;explanation&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;CBT stands for Cognitive Behavioral Therapy.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="3-scoring--achievements"&gt;3. Scoring &amp;amp; Achievements&lt;a class="anchor" href="#3-scoring--achievements"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The quiz engine automatically calculates scores and triggers badges based on performance.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Illustrations</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/design/illustrations/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/design/illustrations/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull uses a hybrid illustration system designed for &lt;strong&gt;speed&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;reliability&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;cinematic polish&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-visual-presentation"&gt;1. Visual Presentation&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-visual-presentation"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All illustrations in MindFull are automatically enhanced by the &lt;strong&gt;Premium Frame Engine&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="course-image-wrapper"&gt;Course Image Wrapper&lt;a class="anchor" href="#course-image-wrapper"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use the &lt;code&gt;.course-image-wrapper&lt;/code&gt; to ensure your visuals match the platform&amp;rsquo;s high-fidelity aesthetic:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🧊 &lt;strong&gt;Squircle Shape&lt;/strong&gt;: Enforces a consistent 3rem rounded &amp;ldquo;Squircle&amp;rdquo; border.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;цент &lt;strong&gt;Perfect Centering&lt;/strong&gt;: Automatically centers SVGs without clipping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎨 &lt;strong&gt;Mesh Background&lt;/strong&gt;: Injects a subtle, dual-radial gradient behind the image.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🚀 &lt;strong&gt;Interactive Scale&lt;/strong&gt;: Automatically scales to 105% on parent card hover.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;course-image-wrapper w-full p-12&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; {{ partial &amp;#34;shared/undraw.html&amp;#34; (dict &amp;#34;name&amp;#34; &amp;#34;meditation&amp;#34;) }}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;div&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-rendering-logic"&gt;2. Rendering Logic&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-rendering-logic"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;undraw.html&lt;/code&gt; partial handles illustrations using a 3-tier &lt;strong&gt;local-first&lt;/strong&gt; strategy.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Public Development</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/development/pubdev/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/development/pubdev/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;If you need to share your local development site with a client or tester, use the &lt;strong&gt;Public Dev&lt;/strong&gt; mode.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="single-command-startup"&gt;Single Command Startup&lt;a class="anchor" href="#single-command-startup"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;npm run pubdev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-it-works"&gt;How it Works&lt;a class="anchor" href="#how-it-works"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote class='book-hint tip'&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This mode uses &lt;strong&gt;Localtunnel&lt;/strong&gt; to generate a public URL instantly with zero registration required.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;h3 id="gateway-routing"&gt;Gateway Routing&lt;a class="anchor" href="#gateway-routing"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Path&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Destination&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Port&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;/api/*&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MindFull CMS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;3000&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;/*&lt;/code&gt; (Root)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hugo Frontend&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;1313&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gateway&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Local Reverse Proxy&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;4242&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3 id="launch-checklist"&gt;Launch Checklist&lt;a class="anchor" href="#launch-checklist"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Run &lt;code&gt;npm run pubdev&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Wait for &lt;code&gt;🔗 SHAREABLE URL&lt;/code&gt; to appear.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Share the URL with your external collaborator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="technical-sequence"&gt;Technical Sequence&lt;a class="anchor" href="#technical-sequence"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proxy Gateway&lt;/strong&gt;: A local proxy starts on port &lt;code&gt;4242&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Public Tunnel&lt;/strong&gt;: Localtunnel creates a secure random URL (e.g., &lt;code&gt;https://random-id.loca.lt&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unified Link&lt;/strong&gt;: Both your Hugo Frontend and CMS Backend are accessible via that single public URL.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description></item><item><title>SSO Configuration</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/getting-started/sso-setup/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/getting-started/sso-setup/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull supports authenticating users via &lt;strong&gt;Google&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;GitHub&lt;/strong&gt;. These services require secure secret management, which is handled by the &lt;strong&gt;MindFull CMS&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-provider-setup"&gt;1. Provider Setup&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-provider-setup"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="google-oauth-setup"&gt;Google OAuth Setup&lt;a class="anchor" href="#google-oauth-setup"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Create a project in the &lt;a href="https://console.cloud.google.com/"&gt;Google Cloud Console&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Navigate to &lt;strong&gt;APIs &amp;amp; Services &amp;gt; Credentials&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Create an &lt;strong&gt;OAuth client ID&lt;/strong&gt; for a &amp;ldquo;Web Application&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Configure the redirect URIs (see table below).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="github-oauth-setup"&gt;GitHub OAuth Setup&lt;a class="anchor" href="#github-oauth-setup"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Go to &lt;a href="https://github.com/settings/developers"&gt;GitHub Developer Settings&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Register a &lt;strong&gt;New OAuth App&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"&gt; Configure the homepage and callback URLs (see table below).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="required-redirect-uris"&gt;Required Redirect URIs&lt;a class="anchor" href="#required-redirect-uris"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Provider&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Environment&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Redirect URI&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Google&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Local&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;http://localhost:3000/api/auth/google/callback&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Local&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;http://localhost:3000/api/auth/github/callback&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-configure-the-cms"&gt;2. Configure the CMS&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-configure-the-cms"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create or edit the &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; file inside the &lt;code&gt;cms/&lt;/code&gt; directory:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Block Library</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/design/blocks/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/design/blocks/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull uses a modular &amp;ldquo;Block&amp;rdquo; architecture. You can build complex, professional pages by simply defining blocks in your markdown frontmatter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-hero-block"&gt;1. Hero Block&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-hero-block"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Hero block is the first thing users see. It&amp;rsquo;s designed for high impact and clear calls to action.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="configuration"&gt;Configuration&lt;a class="anchor" href="#configuration"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;hero]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;tagline = &amp;#34;Your Science-Backed Wellness Journey&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;headline = &amp;#34;Master your mind&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;subheadline = &amp;#34;with daily CBT.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;description = &amp;#34;Learn proven techniques to manage anxiety...&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;illustration = &amp;#34;meditation&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;primaryCta = &amp;#34;Browse Courses&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;primaryCtaLink = &amp;#34;/courses&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;secondaryCta = &amp;#34;Log In&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;secondaryCtaLink = &amp;#34;/login&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="key-properties"&gt;Key Properties&lt;a class="anchor" href="#key-properties"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Property&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th style="text-align: left"&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;tagline&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Small text badge above the headline.&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;illustration&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Slug from the UnDraw library.&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;&lt;code&gt;secondaryCta&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td style="text-align: left"&gt;Automatically hidden if the user is logged in.&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-features-block"&gt;2. Features Block&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-features-block"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Features block displays your value propositions in a clean, responsive grid.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Deployment</title><link>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/getting-started/deployment/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://obsidiansolutions.co.uk/self-help/docs/getting-started/deployment/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;MindFull is architected for maximum stability and performance in production environments.&lt;/p&gt;
